rnal evidence) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33028,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/01\/seek-refuge-entering-masjid\/","url_meta":{"origin":34032,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seek refuge from Satan when entering mosque","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 1, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: When the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the mosque, he would say, \u201cI seek refuge in Allah Almighty, in his noble countenance, and in his everlasting authority from the accursed Satan.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34710,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/21\/refuge-harmful-things\/","url_meta":{"origin":34032,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Seeking refuge from harmful things","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu al-Yasar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, used to supplicate, \u201cO Allah, I seek refuge in You from being crushed under rubble. I seek refuge in You from falling into an abyss. I seek refuge in You from drowning, burning, and senility. I seek\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13739,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/25\/security-asks-bismillah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34032,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Security: Grant refuge to whoever asks by Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 25, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever seeks refuge with you in the name of Allah, grant him refuge. Whoever asks you in the name of Allah, give it to him.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 5109 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Arna'ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37113,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/12\/refuge-in-allah-toilet\/","url_meta":{"origin":34032,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Bathrooms: Refuge in Allah before relieving oneself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 12, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Zayd ibn Arqam reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, these washrooms are inhabited by jinn. When one of you enters his place of relief, let him say: I seek refuge in Allah from foul and noxious things.\u201d Source: Sunan Abi\u0304 Da\u0304wu\u0304d 4 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text